mainText:
A rare few of us may not have known his name until his resignation from Apple, even more do not know him personally, but almost everyone in this world has been affected by what he has done in his lifetime. The impact of his work and passion has been felt by millions all over the planet, and that feeling was definitely a good one. Mr Jobs has made an even greater and more heartfelt influence in our daily lives than most politicians ever will. He has done so much for us, and we will always remember him.

From myself and many more in Singapore, our deepest condolences are extended to his family and friends. His passing is also a great loss to the modern tech community; he is an irreplaceable genius.

May he rest in peace.&nbsp;
